{"tid":1141021,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"原來依家香港去外國嘅旅行團都學埋大陸d濕鳩嘢","createTime":"2019-05-06T08:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T12:55:34.000Z","uid":129013,"like":2,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b21191f83797c7ea1b799d72d0c1646059238701","tid":1141021,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:06:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我一個人第一次去曼谷，又懶得自己搵路就求其join左康泰一個5天團。<br />\n<br />\n埋單連小費4100左右<br />\n<br />\n行程<br />\n第一日: 行程去芭提雅都算係正常，但因為唔包第一日lunch關係，就要自費。呢下就已經伏伏地，走左入去間魚翅店食飯，600B起錶。我屌咩，我算半個環保撚，十年前已經發誓唔食魚翅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後我食咗個600B嘅餐，碗翅畀左團友食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二日睇人妖同Sexy show一切正常<br />\n<br />\n第三日(啫係今日) 芭提雅出曼谷路上就係咁有消費項目前後用左4個鐘去枕頭舖同珠寶店(我依家就係喺間珠寶店度發緊霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n在此想奉勸各位，join旅行團之前真係要問清楚晒每一個鐘嘅行程。 btw以後我都唔會偷懶再報旅行團<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8f467fd9cca856f873197cd5867d3d6faa25d3","tid":1141021,"uid":45645,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"唔肯自遊行, 預咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋康X喺大陸人老闆, 更加伏味濃"},{"pid":"862b076a5c94d8f897d2eba561bebc03a26f42e3","tid":1141021,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e8f467fd9cca856f873197cd5867d3d6faa25d3","tid":1141021,"uid":45645,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"唔肯自遊行, 預咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋康X喺大陸人老闆, 更加伏味濃"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:17:27.000Z","msg":"原來康X嘅老闆是中國人！？<img src=\"/ass